RISK MANAGEMENT
Major Risks & Mitigation:

Quality Issues:

Risk: Receiving damaged/defective vehicles
Mitigation: Always use third-party inspection in Dubai, never skip this; have clear return policies with suppliers
Currency Fluctuation:

Risk: USD/UGX volatility affecting margins
Mitigation: Price in USD or update pricing regularly; hedge with forward contracts for large orders
Regulatory Changes:

Risk: Import duty increases, age restrictions
Mitigation: Stay connected with importers association; diversify to EAC-assembled vehicles; maintain 6-month cash buffer
Payment Default:

Risk: Customers defaulting after vehicle arrival
Mitigation: 40-50% deposit before ordering; clear contracts; legal recourse provisions
Competition:

Risk: Established importers, dealerships
Mitigation: Superior customer service; transparency; competitive pricing; strong online presence
Insurance Coverage Needed:

Marine cargo insurance (for vehicles in transit)
General business insurance
Vehicle stock insurance at yard
Public liability insurance
