CRUCIAL SUCCESS FACTORS
Quality Control: Never compromise on vehicle inspection - your reputation depends on it
Cash Flow Management: Don't overstock; maintain 3-6 months operating expenses
Customer Education: Most buyers don't understand import process - educate them
Transparency: Be honest about timelines, costs, and vehicle condition
Relationships: Strong supplier relationships in Dubai = better deals and priority
Digital Presence: In 2025, no website/social media = you don't exist to many buyers
Patience: First 6 months are about learning and building reputation, not maximum profit
RED FLAGS TO AVOID
Don't pay 100% upfront to Dubai suppliers you haven't verified
Don't skip vehicle inspection to save costs
Don't underestimate import taxes - they're your biggest cost
Don't start without adequate working capital
Don't ignore legal compliance - URA penalties are severe
Don't overpromise delivery timelines
Don't neglect insurance coverage
